{"tid":478350,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"想搵一隻賽車GAME","createTime":"2017-11-24T03:53:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-27T08:53:40.000Z","uid":83375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3332279279600e43cf5b3dc9d0bbbc778ac9c430","tid":478350,"uid":83375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T03:53:23.000Z","msg":"如題，好耐之前玩過，網頁FLASH GAME嚟<br />\n好似ASIADOG玩，但搵極都搵唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n隻GAME有十關，每關用唔同車跑圈數，<br />\n自己跑圈衝線又得，架車夠襟撞可以撞爛其他NPC過關又得<br />\n過關可以解鎖其他車<br />\n<br />\n特別記得第九關會用一架白跑車，<br />\n但有架未被解鎖的綠色卡車會不停撞埋嚟。<br />\n好難先過到哩關，因為經常俾佢追到+撞散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，<br />\n過咗就會解鎖架綠卡車<br />\n<br />\n另外一啲特點就係每圈都有啲位置有個電圈咁嘅嘢，<br />\n飛過穿過就可repair損壞情況<br />\n<br />\n唔知有無兄弟玩過又記得名？<br />\n求被秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"686604b8900522a5849926a7f237dcb608737a46","tid":478350,"uid":116530,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T03:59:39.000Z","msg":"Need for speed"},{"pid":"6dcdd7f747b2a0bd1509d6de318830735101a1f0","tid":478350,"uid":83375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T04:06:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Need for speed</blockquote><br />\n唔係<br />\n<br />\n補充：啲畫質好19，<br />\n啲車呀賽道呀同小畫家畫嘅差不多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db446c1dd1d2bb4f7dc0b682b526504acb9b4645","tid":478350,"uid":83375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T04:45:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e2ae6af3ba624acdb502d85124e64de37cb3930","tid":478350,"uid":83375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"